text: Jiangxi Hanteng Automobile Co., Ltd or Hanteng Autos was a privately owned Chinese automobile company headquartered in Shangrao, Jiangxi. It made and sold traditional fuel-powered vehicles, new energy vehicles, EVs and automotive parts. It was founded in November 2013, and went defunct in 2022 due to its bankruptcy. == Models == * Hanteng X5 * Hanteng X5 EV * Hanteng X7 * Hanteng X7S * Hanteng X7 PHEV * Hanteng X8 * Hanteng V7 == References == Category:Automobile companies of China
